{"ja474:0.1":"Jataka ","ja474:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja474:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja474:0.4":"1. Ambajataka ","ja474:1.1":"“Ahasi me ambaphalani pubbe, ","ja474:1.2":"Anuni thulani ca brahmacari; ","ja474:1.3":"Teheva mantehi na dani tuyham, ","ja474:1.4":"Dumapphala patubhavanti brahme”. ","ja474:2.1":"“Nakkhattayogam patimanayami, ","ja474:2.2":"Khanam muhuttanca mante na passam; ","ja474:2.3":"Nakkhattayoganca khananca laddha, ","ja474:2.4":"Addhaharissambaphalam pahutam”. ","ja474:3.1":"“Nakkhattayogam na pure abhani, ","ja474:3.2":"Khanam muhuttam na pure asamsi; ","ja474:3.3":"Sayam hari ambaphalam pahutam, ","ja474:3.4":"Vannena gandhena rasenupetam. ","ja474:4.1":"Mantabhijappena pure hi tuyham, ","ja474:4.2":"Dumapphala patubhavanti brahme; ","ja474:4.3":"Svajja na paresi jappampi mantam, ","ja474:4.4":"Ayam so ko nama tavajja dhammo”. ","ja474:5.1":"“Candalaputto mama sampadasi, ","ja474:5.2":"Dhammena mante pakatinca samsi; ","ja474:5.3":"Ma cassu me pucchito namagottam, ","ja474:5.4":"Guyhittho attham vijaheyya manto. ","ja474:6.1":"Soham janindena janamhi puttho, ","ja474:6.2":"Makkhabhibhuto alikam abhanim; ","ja474:6.3":"‘Manta ime brahmanassa’ti miccha, ","ja474:6.4":"Pahinamanto kapano rudami”. ","ja474:7.1":"“Eranda pucimanda va, ","ja474:7.2":"atha va palibhaddaka; ","ja474:7.3":"Madhum madhutthiko vinde, ","ja474:7.4":"so hi tassa dumuttamo. ","ja474:8.1":"Khattiya brahmana vessa, ","ja474:8.2":"sudda candalapukkusa; ","ja474:8.3":"Yamha dhammam vijaneyya, ","ja474:8.4":"so hi tassa naruttamo. ","ja474:9.1":"Imassa dandanca vadhanca datva, ","ja474:9.2":"Gale gahetva khalayatha jammam; ","ja474:9.3":"Yo uttamattham kasirena laddham, ","ja474:9.4":"Manatimanena vinasayittha”. ","ja474:10.1":"“Yatha samam mannamano pateyya, ","ja474:10.2":"Sobbham guham narakam putipadam; ","ja474:10.3":"Rajjuti va akkame kanhasappam, ","ja474:10.4":"Andho yatha jotimadhitthaheyya; ","ja474:10.5":"Evampi mam tvam khalitam sapanna, ","ja474:10.6":"Pahinamantassa punappadahi”. ","ja474:11.1":"“Dhammena mantam tava sampadasim, ","ja474:11.2":"Tuvampi dhammena pariggahesi; ","ja474:11.3":"Pakatimpi te attamano asamsim, ","ja474:11.4":"Dhamme thitam tam na jaheyya manto. ","ja474:12.1":"Yo bala mantam kasirena laddham, ","ja474:12.2":"Yam dullabham ajja manussaloke; ","ja474:12.3":"Kincapi laddha jivitum appapanno, ","ja474:12.4":"Vinasayi alikam bhasamano. ","ja474:13.1":"Balassa mulhassa akatannuno ca, ","ja474:13.2":"Musa bhanantassa asannatassa; ","ja474:13.3":"Mante mayam tadisake na dema, ","ja474:13.4":"Kuto manta gaccha na mayha ruccasi”ti. ","ja474:14.1":"Ambajatakam pathamam. "}